				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BB%93i-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-%C4%91%C4%83ng-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-s%C6%A1n-t%E1%BB%91i-cao-%C4%91%E1%BB%89nh-y%E1%BA%BFn-Di%C3%AAu-Th%C3%B4ng-Tuy%E1%BB%81n-v%C3%A3n-hu%E1%BB%81-t%E1%BB%ADu-phi%E1%BA%BFm-giang/poem-zeOhhMM1duWEshoMtUybtQ">Bồi Vương thị ngự đồng đăng Đông sơn tối cao đỉnh, yến Diêu Thông Tuyền, vãn huề tửu phiếm giang - 陪王侍禦同登東山最高頂宴姚通泉，晚攜酒泛江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-V%E1%BB%8B/Cung-y%E1%BA%BFt-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-L%C4%83ng-ch%C3%ADnh-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-HLP8j8tNIitVO827LlL6_w">Cung yết Hiếu Lăng chính vận - 恭謁孝陵正韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-V%E1%BB%8B/author-cFaiJWajT_3vfsAWKg1raQ">Từ Vị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/%C4%90%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93-Tri%E1%BB%87u-Vi%C3%AAm-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7-ph%E1%BA%A5n-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-s%C6%A1n-thu%E1%BB%B7-ca/poem-QP2kBK_qLMSsvg269jP2kA">Đương Đồ Triệu Viêm thiếu phủ phấn đồ sơn thuỷ ca - 當涂趙炎少府粉圖山水歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ho%E1%BA%A1-M%C3%ADnh-Vi%C3%AAn-Hu%E1%BB%B3nh-Th%C3%BAc-Kh%C3%A1ng-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-T%C3%A2n-T%E1%BB%B5-th%C3%AD-b%C3%BAt-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-a48YulUUmyeQjrnsU1Um-g">Hoạ Mính Viên Huỳnh Thúc Kháng tiên sinh Tân Tỵ thí bút nguyên vận - 和茗園黃叔沆先生辛巳試筆原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%E1%BB%87p-M%E1%BB%99ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%AFc/Thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-ca-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-C%E1%BB%ADu-nguy%E1%BB%87t-v%E1%BB%8Dng-nh%E1%BA%ADt-d%E1%BB%AF-kh%C3%A1ch-t%E1%BA%ADp-x%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%A2y-vi%C3%AAn-d%C6%B0-b%E1%BB%87nh-b%E1%BA%A5t-n%C4%83ng-x%E1%BA%A1/poem-j9hvBEuD6ZYnyKHm86BNPA">Thuỷ điệu ca đầu - Cửu nguyệt vọng nhật, dữ khách tập xạ tây viên, dư bệnh bất năng xạ - 水調歌頭－九月望日，與客習射西園，餘病不能射</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%E1%BB%87p-M%E1%BB%99ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%AFc/author-uvmozYn2LwhrrzPcBoMwnQ">Diệp Mộng Đắc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Ph%C3%B9ng/Tu%C3%BD-trung-v%C4%83n-Cam-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-MRFXn7OobyvsFXF9rXoUAw">Tuý trung văn Cam Châu - 醉中聞甘州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Ph%C3%B9ng/author-2lovo1tul_9ix8CytGMv0Q">Tiết Phùng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/U-gi%E1%BA%A3n-tuy%E1%BB%81n/poem-EWXqNfXDGvE8oGnx69xyyQ">U giản tuyền - 幽澗泉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C3%A3ng-t%E1%BA%A1i/poem-7mMhxNkbIYnhoXxZ2p4JlA">Vãng tại - 往在</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/V%C3%B5ng-Xuy%C3%AAn-nh%C3%A0n-c%C6%B0-t%E1%BA%B7ng-B%C3%B9i-t%C3%BA-t%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-y9gZometdRFUsWlAUMEwMg">Võng Xuyên nhàn cư tặng Bùi tú tài Địch - 輞川閑居贈裴秀才迪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/Vu-gi%C3%A1p-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-vi%C3%AAn-ca-t%E1%BB%91ng-Kh%C3%A2u-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7-quy-T%E1%BB%A9-Minh/poem-YjAumCpF734xGxZXFgBoNA">Vu giáp đề viên ca tống Khâu thiếu phủ quy Tứ Minh - 巫峽啼猿歌送丘少府歸四明</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/author-og0yg1YWgltsRxS7PoXrcQ">Lâm Hồng</a>)<br></div>	</div>
